resources.string: The Consulate-General of Japan (CGJ) has requested that we provide them with information about JET alumni living within their jurisdiction. PNWJETAA will have no control over how the Consulate uses your information should you choose to share it with them. Please choose from one of the following options.
Yes, PNWJETAA can share the information I provide on this form with the CGJ
No, PNWJETAA cannot share the information I provide on this form with the CGJ
